---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';

// === Sony: This Moment, faithful rebuild of monuments.cc/portfolio/sony-this-moment ===
// Real campaign stills pulled from the live site into /public/case-studies/sony-this-moment.
const g = Array.from({ length: 9 }, (_, i) => `/case-studies/sony-this-moment/gallery/tm-${String(i + 1).padStart(2, '0')}.jpg`);
const meta = [
  { k: 'Client', v: 'Sony Audio' },
  { k: 'Agency', v: 'Art of Visuals' },
  { k: 'Production', v: 'MGX Creative' },
  { k: 'Director', v: 'Daniel Malikyar' },
  { k: 'Creative Direction', v: 'DJ Ramirez' },
  { k: 'Stills', v: 'Claire LeJune' },
];
---
<Base title="Sony: This Moment · monuments">
  <article class="bc-page">

    <!-- HERO (full-bleed image) -->
    <header class="bc-hero">
      <img class="bc-hero-img" src={g[8]} alt="Sony: This Moment campaign" />
      <div class="bc-hero-inner">
        <p class="bc-hero-eyebrow">Sony Audio · Creative Direction</p>
        <h1 class="bc-hero-title">This Moment</h1>
        <p class="bc-hero-lede">This moment is for you.</p>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- INTRO -->
    <section class="bc-intro fade">
      <p>Feeling overwhelmed shouldn't be the norm, but it's a feeling we can all relate to. When the world gets noisy, headphones aren't just a piece of tech, they're a device for creating an environment, a moment of peace and serenity no matter where you are or what may be happening around you.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- CAMPAIGN SHOT -->
    <figure class="bc-shot fade">
      <img src={g[0]} alt="Sony: This Moment, a moment of peace" loading="lazy" />
    </figure>

    <!-- INSIGHT QUOTE -->
    <section class="bc-quote fade">
      <p>True creativity flourishes when given <span class="bc-quote-em">the space to breathe</span> and align with the natural flow of inspiration.</p>
      <p class="bc-quote-attr">The idea behind the campaign.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- CAMPAIGN PAIR -->
    <div class="bc-duo fade">
      <img src={g[1]} alt="Sony: This Moment" loading="lazy" />
      <img src={g[2]} alt="Sony: This Moment" loading="lazy" />
    </div>

    <!-- EXECUTION -->
    <section class="bc-exec fade">
      <h2 class="bc-exec-h">Trusting the process.</h2>
      <div class="bc-exec-b">
        <p>Sony partnered with Art of Visuals to craft a campaign that underscores the value of taking time, trusting the process, and rediscovering inspiration. This initiative encourages creators to embrace moments of pause, demonstrating that true creativity flourishes when given the space to breathe.</p>
        <p>As the creative director on this project, I helped shape the story, wrote the briefs, directed the stills, and made sure everything on set matched Sony's brand guides. I also worked closely with the production team through post, giving feedback on edits and prepping files for delivery. We cut the videos down from one minute to 30- and 15-second ads, and the stills ran as display advertising.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SECOND SHOT -->
    <figure class="bc-shot fade">
      <img src={g[3]} alt="Sony: This Moment, on set" loading="lazy" />
    </figure>

    <!-- CAMPAIGN PAIR 2 -->
    <div class="bc-duo fade">
      <img src={g[4]} alt="Sony: This Moment" loading="lazy" />
      <img src={g[5]} alt="Sony: This Moment" loading="lazy" />
    </div>

    <!-- FINAL SHOT -->
    <figure class="bc-shot fade">
      <img src={g[7]} alt="Sony: This Moment" loading="lazy" />
    </figure>

    <!-- META -->
    <div class="bc-meta fade">
      {meta.map((m) => (
        <div class="cs-meta-item">
          <span class="cs-meta-k">{m.k}</span>
          <span class="cs-meta-v">{m.v}</span>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <!-- NEXT -->
    <a class="cs-next" href="/work/sony-flow-state">
      <span class="cs-next-k">Next project</span>
      <span class="cs-next-t">Sony: Flow State <span class="cs-next-arrow">→</span></span>
    </a>

  </article>
</Base>
